For this project to work, the system needs to be able to collect live LP (liquidity pool) data, process it using my logic, and respond to the user via Telegram in real-time. So I’ve broken it down into what’s needed for both the backend system (the code and processing) and the data side (everything the system needs to make allocation decisions).

